{"word":"G346 - ἀνακεφαλαίομαι - anakephalaíomai - an-ak-ef-al-ah'-ee-om-ahee - Briefly comprehend","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀνακεφαλαίομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">anakephalaíomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-ak-ef-al-ah'-ee-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Briefly comprehend</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அடங்கு, கூட்டு"},{"paragraph":"to sum up (again), to repeat summarily and so to condense into a summary"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G303 - ἀνά - aná - an-ah'/303\">G303</a> and <a href=\"#/G2775 - κεφαλαιόω - kephalaióō - kef-al-ahee-o'-o/2775\">G2775</a> (in its original sense); to <i>sum up:</i> - briefly comprehend, gather together in one.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2774/2774\">G2774</a>, <a href=\"#/G2775/2775\">G2775</a>, <a href=\"#/G2776/2776\">G2776</a>, <a href=\"#/G346/346\">G346</a>"}]}